Industries: Blockchain, Cryptocurrency, Financial Services, Loyalty Programs
Description: LoyalCoin offers a customer loyalty-oriented digital asset that is replacing and enhancing traditional rewards point systems.
Full Description: LoyalCoin is redefining customer loyalty by leading the loyalty economy into the blockchain-fueled future. LoyalCoin is the customer loyalty-oriented digital asset that is replacing and enhancing the traditional rewards point systems we currently have. Like a traditional rewards point, LoyalCoin can be used to redeem rewards from any participating merchant. That way, your points from one merchant can be redeemed on every other merchant within the system. However, LoyalCoin can also be sent to and received from other people, used as payment for a user’s preferred merchant, and more. LoyalCoin can be stored in the LoyalWallet, an app that enables the digital asset’s redemption, payment, and more features. LoyalCoin can also be stored in white label apps we're developing for participating merchants; these apps will carry a few of the features that LoyalWallet has. As LoyalCoin is also a NEM token, it can also be stored in any of the NEM official wallets. Upon the public launch of LoyalCoin and LoyalWallet, users earn LoyalCoin by buying products and services from merchants and shops that issue LoyalCoin, just like the way you earn points at a typical rewards program. In addition, as discussed above, the LoyalWallet allows you to buy more LoyalCoin.

It empowers students throughout different stages of their educational journey so that it leads them to a fulfilling career and life. Edge Tutor is a fully online high dosage tutoring service that provides K-12 students with high quality academic support from certified tutors. With courses ranging from Math, English to Filipino, sessions are designed to give each student a personalized and engaging learning experience -- all at very affordable price.  With Empower, Edukasyon partners with hundreds of educational institutions, corporations and foundations, to equip the youth with information and life skills to help them create and shape their own paths, as they discover more about themselves and the opportunities available to them. Finally, with Explore, Edukasyon provides a free online platform that enables students to access senior high schools, colleges and universities, scholarships, online courses, internships, and other learning resources. Edukasyon.ph, which also operates the website FindUniversity (www.finduniversity.ph) engages more than 8 million learners each year. Edukasyon.ph is supported in part by impact investors, family offices and angel investors across Asia, Europe and North America, including Mustard Seed, Villgro Philippines, French Partners, KSR Ventures, Gobi-Core Philippine Fund, EduLab Capital Partners, Obunsha Ventures, Alternate Ventures, Foxmont Capital Partners, Lorinet Foundation, Bisk Ventures and First Asia Venture Capital. Edukasyon.ph has received several recognitions for its work, including the 2017 Financial Times / IFC Transformational Business Award for Achievement in Sustainable Development, with a focus on Education, Knowledge and Skills, as well as the 2017 ASEAN Youth Social Entrepreneurship Awards. Edukasyon.ph was also included in the 2016 World Innovation Summit for Education (WISE) Accelerator Program. Launched in 2015, Edukasyon.ph now has a team of more than 50 and is headquartered in Manila. For more information, visit www.edukasyon.ph.

Description: ShoreAgents: BPO specializing in virtual staff for real estate. Dedicated remote team from our office to serve your business needs.
Full Description: ShoreAgents was created by Stephen Atcheler, a successful real estate business owner who discovered the benefits of hiring talented staff from the Philippines. He started with just one team member and quickly grew his team into a competitive force that left his rivals wondering how he was achieving so much. Drawing from his experience, Atcheler developed a unique approach to outsourcing that sets ShoreAgents apart from other BPO companies. One of the key factors that contribute to ShoreAgents' success is their recruitment strategy. Unlike other BPOs, ShoreAgents doesn't just hand over any resume to their clients. They process over 1000 candidates every month and attract them through embodied methods, not just online job portals. They filter and test every candidate, complete full professional reference checks, and have them do a video introduction to ensure they are suitable for the role. Once they pass the tests, ShoreAgents sets up a company interview and guides the clients through the process to ensure they choose the right person. But their unique approach doesn't stop there. ShoreAgents has a three-tiered performance measuring approach that ensures their staff are performing at their best. They conduct weekly check-ins with the staff, monthly catch-ups, and performance reviews conducted by the clients themselves. Moreover, their dedicated success team is always on hand to help with anything the clients need, from process to buying birthday cakes for their team. They take care of all other aspects so that the clients can focus on making their team members more productive and growing their business. What sets ShoreAgents apart from other BPO companies is their focus on staff retention, motivation, and engagement. They foster a positive and engaging work culture that motivates their team members to perform at their best and stay with the company for the long term. They offer a range of perks and benefits, from monthly games and team-building events to free lunches and travel opportunities. Their focus on staff retention means that clients can rely on them to provide highly skilled and committed agents for their outsourcing needs. ShoreAgents' success in the outsourcing journey is guaranteed, and they offer a standout deal that ensures clients' success without compromising on quality. Choosing the cheapest service may actually end up costing more in the long run, but with ShoreAgents, clients can be confident that their team is motivated and committed to delivering outstanding results for their business. Whether clients need help with a complex task or simply want to streamline their operations, ShoreAgents' success team is here to support them every step of the way. Choose ShoreAgents for a successful outsourcing journey that exceeds expectations.

Description: JustPayto is a technology company that enables digital payments and money transfers for individuals and businesses.
Full Description: JustPayto is a technology company that enables digital payments and money transfers for individuals and businesses.  JustPayto offers convenient inter-bank, inter-institution, inter-platform, inter-currency money transfers. The company creates a frictionless ecosystem with any bank, any financial institution, and any e-wallet. The company makes traditional cash-based and digital cash-less payment methods work together – credit/debit cards, bank fund transfer, online banking, over-the-counter, e-wallet, and cryptocurrency.  JustPayto is a money transfer platform that provides inter-bank, inter-platform, and inter-currency transactions, merging traditional and digital forms of financial services. JustPayto provides a platform for cash-based and cash-less transactions and financial services. JustPayto's online payment platform connects to payment methods across the world. Payment methods include international credit cards, local cash-based methods, and internet banking methods. The technology platform acts as a payment aggregator, payment gateway, payment service provider and offers technology solutions to digitize bank offerings such as escrow, loans, and business services. JustPayto is built on the existing financial infrastructure of bank accounts and credit cards to create a global, robust, and reliable money transfer solution. JustPayto delivers a product ideal for the banked, unbanked, and underbanked. The company's combined payment solutions, including its Payment Address, Payment Page, Pay Button, Invoicing, QR Codes, Mass Payouts, Cash Card, Mobile Apps, Escrow, Logistics, Payment Gateway, Developer API and Business Services, compose its ecosystem, built on top of its Payments Platform. The Company operates a two-sided global technology platform that links its customers, both merchants/recipients (account holders) and consumers/senders (end user), around the globe to facilitate the processing of payment transactions, allowing it to connect merchants and consumers.
